[{"Code":"en","Title":"Optimizing operations","Slug":"optimizing-operations","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"0d83e324-6b18-4d15-9efa-215c7ff3db88\">Learn how to reduce your customer complaints and help your customer inquiries. This page will guide you through some best practices that would allow you to achieve operational excellence. </p><h2 data-block-id=\"c9b5c42b-7fb9-4e9d-9ffb-f19e2b597276\">Common operation issues</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"708aa0a6-59ab-47c7-803d-267b9cad4868\">Funds not received</h3><p data-block-id=\"8fed5d84-96fa-4280-82a7-c06179f1701e\">Due to messaging issues, your recipient might get back to you saying that the funds have not been received. To help with this process, we recommend that you:</p><ul data-block-id=\"328d892c-175c-4048-bb61-99fc0e52fc9a\"><li data-block-id=\"20f947d2-6842-4a8f-823d-0495c84eaf40\"><p data-block-id=\"d6da130f-97f7-4a53-a48b-9f8eb59b5f4a\">Subscribe to payout webhooks for latest status updates and auto recovery</p></li><li data-block-id=\"0ae03ab7-2e91-4d5b-80c1-3894a3cf136d\"><p data-block-id=\"547eeb2a-72ab-4914-8cef-6f594efd1907\">Send Payout receipt to your recipient for them to track and log an issue with their bank</p></li><li data-block-id=\"6215d941-16e6-497e-81ba-7dad28118b06\"><p data-block-id=\"2735f089-916e-4803-bb1a-cce10c82d74e\">Utilize <code>description</code> to send identifiers to your recipient’s app or statement</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"ecf72a0f-91f0-44af-adb0-74938842ddd5\">Funds bounced back</h3><p data-block-id=\"1bfa13ca-e548-4e9b-a5d4-ba31b0a62e29\">Sometimes we cannot pay the funds out or the funds are returned to us due to processing limitations (e.g. the recipient’s details were incorrect or their account is closed). We recommend that you:</p><ul data-block-id=\"b2a183d0-6f95-426c-98aa-44ddc90b04db\"><li data-block-id=\"487082c5-870e-4121-8c67-ce5d06a67d1e\"><p data-block-id=\"6627dc47-93a4-46ee-a860-beeca688ab70\">Subscribe to reversed/failed webhooks for latest status updates</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"f49c69e3-b5ec-437b-a919-6c48b6082cd2\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"8f796388-25e8-4452-aa55-ba5da3e1e6e7\">Tool for reducing operations issues</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"7910962d-e6f6-43d5-a28c-55b7db6f5ce9\">Payout receipts</h3><p data-block-id=\"be7bce22-a700-4a12-9bc3-602101dd205b\">Payout receipts is a simple yet powerful tool to assure your recipient that the funds has been processed, and if not yet received, is on its way to their account. If utilized, we will send this on behalf of you directly to your recipient on successful payout processing.</p><h4 data-block-id=\"ee899a45-9973-4b5d-8357-5537c33ca90b\">Brand your payout receipt to build more trust</h4><p data-block-id=\"bfd422d7-15cc-449f-b181-0db2e891360c\">Personalize receipts with your business logo. By default, the business logo on your profile will be displayed.</p><ol data-block-id=\"760d138c-d367-4f55-8faf-68ecdaf3465e\" start=\"1\" style=\"\" data-indent=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"19c726fb-f196-4fdb-b6cb-e3c75414c13f\"><p data-block-id=\"fe5911ff-a94f-46db-b7cf-1676ce3c028b\">Log in to your dashboard</p></li><li data-block-id=\"540a84e4-f40b-40bb-bc5d-bb963010121f\"><p data-block-id=\"3cba473c-8e47-4873-93d7-b7449b968c64\">Go to Settings &gt; <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/business-profile#business\" translate=\"no\">Edit Profile</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"f4f1a71f-bae0-4ba7-87a4-a0c4fa89a0f2\"><p data-block-id=\"acc1c727-c3dd-4ae8-8e94-415248fa417d\">Click Upload Business Logo</p></li></ol><h4 data-block-id=\"93b06bc9-41b6-4c6a-b3c6-f3ef32dafef9\">Provide a helpline for your users</h4><ol data-block-id=\"99189ec8-0755-4943-a115-1b1ff2d63e20\" start=\"1\" style=\"\"><li data-block-id=\"3fee97e3-8dfa-4894-9569-235f0300d5a3\"><p data-block-id=\"885e025f-dad6-44a7-9880-d7eccee8164f\">Log in to your dashboard</p></li><li data-block-id=\"d7be3adc-3a29-4c9b-9fc9-d680d6b94a0b\"><p data-block-id=\"e9066016-6eba-458e-9896-ec06087d18bd\">Go to <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/sending-money#disbursement-notifications\" translate=\"no\">Disbursement Notifications Settings</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"61334aaa-c028-461b-abfd-fd23ada9c4f2\"><p data-block-id=\"e0d91721-b1c5-47e4-91e7-d328777c1aea\">In the Disbursement Email Template or Batch Disbursement Email Template section, you can enter the information displayed to the end user in the email footer</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"ffd3a5bc-bf12-4e06-a966-0e65c7c1869a\"><img data-block-id=\"4399aa04-92eb-46eb-932f-d0f3243fdaaa\" src=\"https://archive.docs.xendit.co/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fres.cloudinary.com%2Fdpvzoteik%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fc_fill%2Ch_330%2Cw_1598%2FScreenshot_2023-12-06_at_15.15.00_ws6m3c%3F_a%3DBATCr5fi0&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border:0px solid rgb(229, 231, 235);--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-color:rgba(59,130,246,.5);--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;display:block;vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;margin-top:2em;margin-bottom:2em;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;color:transparent;width:1125px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"4e7cbae7-d6c8-4138-b08d-197b4df66e3d\"></p><h3 data-block-id=\"894aa43a-5e59-4212-be19-54e27e1a2db4\">Resend payout receipts</h3><p data-block-id=\"c6ac5423-f91f-4ca3-8ea4-165b7bac58d5\">Easily resend payout receipts from your dashboard to share with recipients as proof of transfer.</p><h4 data-block-id=\"f28c0e8e-31f2-457c-9f89-32b608b0cda1\">Payouts API</h4><ol data-block-id=\"7d0e64a7-d224-4212-a81e-41e2a62b32eb\" start=\"1\" style=\"\"><li data-block-id=\"298b8f1b-cb8d-4e9a-b2fa-45d96d7a0e2a\"><p data-block-id=\"93f4e629-2433-4eb9-b025-c2aededbd6cd\">Go to <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/transactions-new\" translate=\"no\">Transactions</a> on your dashboard</p></li><li data-block-id=\"76f1a087-ec25-4634-bcdc-4d65bc887d60\"><p data-block-id=\"9a3989bd-b2e5-4173-86ae-94ab3a53bb9f\">Click on the completed transaction</p></li><li data-block-id=\"f9b04ec6-cf23-48b8-8110-8f2c76be9a54\"><p data-block-id=\"06ce5eca-76e0-45e0-8c61-7737c43bec87\">Scroll down to Payout Receipt and click Send Receipt</p></li><li data-block-id=\"753ab440-5065-40d7-8a1a-0afb408fd7ea\"><p data-block-id=\"ca238ff1-8742-4241-ba89-9fe5124707ae\">Enter your recipient's email</p></li></ol><h4 data-block-id=\"c56028c6-6b5e-4654-9603-45c498ee6c11\">Batch Payouts</h4><ol data-block-id=\"8e03f680-bd9c-46e6-9708-c274f00135a6\" start=\"1\" style=\"\"><li data-block-id=\"17afcbf7-bb2a-4c63-9901-b0cf8d0f2940\"><p data-block-id=\"950bfd8a-4a57-49b5-95de-68f144437d00\">Go to <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/dashboard/batch_disbursements\" translate=\"no\">Batch Payouts &gt; Approved</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"219cd9ef-eaa2-4946-b1c1-513133371976\"><p data-block-id=\"a0366aad-aebe-434d-9718-03d7c7316074\">Click on a batch payout</p></li><li data-block-id=\"d8353d4a-deb1-4604-bc73-e3b4ca773d01\"><p data-block-id=\"e80bd9a0-998c-4d63-94dd-d059458e99a0\">Export all or selected receipts</p><ol data-block-id=\"e7c2fecb-8248-469b-a6a8-44052e9a2c7c\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"96f4b0db-6dc9-4c14-a3b5-4d255653f337\"><p data-block-id=\"ee6bfdcb-a277-491c-9a0d-e45c1d498d1b\">For all: Click Export Receipt &gt; All Completed</p></li><li data-block-id=\"9443c5ad-54ca-43c5-9670-4d4fb4a8234e\"><p data-block-id=\"ebd2275e-e96c-459d-8fb1-40abf7735f92\">For selected: Select transactions, then click Export Receipt &gt; Selected</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"329a631a-3d5e-4c05-9da5-c47ac053a665\"><p data-block-id=\"2b396333-0089-4d42-9665-da1f0dffe304\">A download link (valid for 7 days) will be emailed to you</p></li><li data-block-id=\"7b0a2bcf-1201-4633-b7c0-330256448068\"><p data-block-id=\"665153cb-cf6f-4e4f-9518-dfbf4e07d7d2\">Open the email and click to download your receipt(s)</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"3caf28b2-b858-46f7-8280-2b144edeb637\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Optimizing operations","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Optimalisasi operasional","Slug":"operations-guide","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"0d83e324-6b18-4d15-9efa-215c7ff3db88\">Pelajari cara mengurangi keluhan pelanggan dan membantu pertanyaan pelanggan Anda. Halaman ini akan memandu Anda melalui beberapa praktik terbaik yang akan memungkinkan Anda mencapai keunggulan operasional.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"c9b5c42b-7fb9-4e9d-9ffb-f19e2b597276\">Masalah operasional umum</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"708aa0a6-59ab-47c7-803d-267b9cad4868\">Dana tidak diterima</h3><p data-block-id=\"8fed5d84-96fa-4280-82a7-c06179f1701e\">Karena masalah pengiriman pesan, penerima Anda mungkin menghubungi Anda kembali dan mengatakan bahwa dana belum diterima. Untuk membantu proses ini, kami menyarankan Anda untuk:</p><ul data-block-id=\"328d892c-175c-4048-bb61-99fc0e52fc9a\"><li data-block-id=\"20f947d2-6842-4a8f-823d-0495c84eaf40\"><p data-block-id=\"d6da130f-97f7-4a53-a48b-9f8eb59b5f4a\">Berlangganan webhook payout untuk pembaruan status terkini dan pemulihan otomatis</p></li><li data-block-id=\"0ae03ab7-2e91-4d5b-80c1-3894a3cf136d\"><p data-block-id=\"547eeb2a-72ab-4914-8cef-6f594efd1907\">Kirim bukti pembayaran Payout kepada penerima Anda agar mereka dapat melacak dan melaporkan masalah ke bank mereka</p></li><li data-block-id=\"6215d941-16e6-497e-81ba-7dad28118b06\"><p data-block-id=\"2735f089-916e-4803-bb1a-cce10c82d74e\">Gunakan <code>description</code> untuk mengirim pengidentifikasi ke aplikasi atau laporan rekening penerima Anda</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"ecf72a0f-91f0-44af-adb0-74938842ddd5\">Dana dikembalikan</h3><p data-block-id=\"1bfa13ca-e548-4e9b-a5d4-ba31b0a62e29\">Terkadang kami tidak dapat membayarkan dana atau dana dikembalikan kepada kami karena keterbatasan pemrosesan (misalnya, detail penerima salah atau akun mereka ditutup). Kami menyarankan Anda untuk:</p><ul data-block-id=\"b2a183d0-6f95-426c-98aa-44ddc90b04db\"><li data-block-id=\"487082c5-870e-4121-8c67-ce5d06a67d1e\"><p data-block-id=\"6627dc47-93a4-46ee-a860-beeca688ab70\">Berlangganan webhook untuk dana yang dikembalikan/gagal (reversed/failed) untuk pembaruan status terkini</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"f49c69e3-b5ec-437b-a919-6c48b6082cd2\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"8f796388-25e8-4452-aa55-ba5da3e1e6e7\">Alat untuk mengurangi masalah operasional</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"7910962d-e6f6-43d5-a28c-55b7db6f5ce9\">Bukti pembayaran payout</h3><p data-block-id=\"be7bce22-a700-4a12-9bc3-602101dd205b\">Bukti pembayaran payout adalah alat yang sederhana namun kuat untuk meyakinkan penerima Anda bahwa dana telah diproses, dan jika belum diterima, sedang dalam perjalanan ke akun mereka. Jika digunakan, kami akan mengirimkannya atas nama Anda langsung ke penerima Anda setelah pemrosesan payout berhasil.</p><h4 data-block-id=\"ee899a45-9973-4b5d-8357-5537c33ca90b\">Beri merek pada bukti pembayaran payout Anda untuk membangun lebih banyak kepercayaan</h4><p data-block-id=\"bfd422d7-15cc-449f-b181-0db2e891360c\">Personalisasi bukti pembayaran dengan logo bisnis Anda. Secara default, logo bisnis di profil Anda akan ditampilkan.</p><ol data-block-id=\"760d138c-d367-4f55-8faf-68ecdaf3465e\" start=\"1\" style data-indent=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"19c726fb-f196-4fdb-b6cb-e3c75414c13f\"><p data-block-id=\"fe5911ff-a94f-46db-b7cf-1676ce3c028b\">Masuk ke dashboard Anda</p></li><li data-block-id=\"540a84e4-f40b-40bb-bc5d-bb963010121f\"><p data--block-id=\"3cba473c-8e47-4873-93d7-b7449b968c64\">Buka Pengaturan &gt; <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/business-profile#business\" translate=\"no\">Edit Profil</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"f4f1a71f-bae0-4ba7-87a4-a0c4fa89a0f2\"><p data-block-id=\"acc1c727-c3dd-4ae8-8e94-415248fa417d\">Klik Unggah Logo Bisnis</p></li></ol><h4 data-block-id=\"93b06bc9-41b6-4c6a-b3c6-f3ef32dafef9\">Sediakan saluran bantuan untuk pengguna Anda</h4><ol data-block-id=\"99189ec8-0755-4943-a115-1b1ff2d63e20\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"3fee97e3-8dfa-4894-9569-235f0300d5a3\"><p data-block-id=\"885e025f-dad6-44a7-9880-d7eccee8164f\">Masuk ke dashboard Anda</p></li><li data-block-id=\"d7be3adc-3a29-4c9b-9fc9-d680d6b94a0b\"><p data-block-id=\"e9066016-6eba-458e-9896-ec06087d18bd\">Buka <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/sending-money#disbursement-notifications\" translate=\"no\">Pengaturan Notifikasi Pencairan Dana</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"61334aaa-c028-461b-abfd-fd23ada9c4f2\"><p data-block-id=\"e0d91721-b1c5-47e4-91e7-d328777c1aea\">Di bagian Templat Email Pencairan Dana atau Templat Email Pencairan Dana Batch, Anda dapat memasukkan informasi yang ditampilkan kepada pengguna akhir di footer email</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"ffd3a5bc-bf12-4e06-a966-0e65c7c1869a\"><img data-block-id=\"4399aa04-92eb-46eb-932f-d0f3243fdaaa\" src=\"https://archive.docs.xendit.co/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fres.cloudinary.com%2Fdpvzoteik%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fc_fill%2Ch_330%2Cw_1598%2FScreenshot_2023-12-06_at_15.15.00_ws6m3c%253F_a%253DBATCr5fi0&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border:0px solid rgb(229, 231, 235);--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-color:rgba(59,130,246,.5);--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;display:block;vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;margin-top:2em;margin-bottom:2em;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;color:transparent;width:1125px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"4e7cbae7-d6c8-4138-b08d-197b4df66e3d\"></p><h3 data-block-id=\"894aa43a-5e59-4212-be19-54e27e1a2db4\">Kirim ulang bukti pembayaran payout</h3><p data-block-id=\"c6ac5423-f91f-4ca3-8ea4-165b7bac58d5\">Kirim ulang bukti pembayaran payout dengan mudah dari dashboard Anda untuk dibagikan kepada penerima sebagai bukti transfer.</p><h4 data-block-id=\"f28c0e8e-31f2-457c-9f89-32b608b0cda1\">API Payouts</h4><ol data-block-id=\"7d0e64a7-d224-4212-a81e-41e2a62b32eb\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"298b8f1b-cb8d-4e9a-b2fa-45d96d7a0e2a\"><p data-block-id=\"93f4e629-2433-4eb9-b025-c2aededbd6cd\">Buka <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/transactions-new\" translate=\"no\">Transaksi</a> di dashboard Anda</p></li><li data-block-id=\"76f1a087-ec25-4634-bcdc-4d65bc887d60\"><p data-block-id=\"9a3989bd-b2e5-4173-86ae-94ab3a53bb9f\">Klik pada transaksi yang telah selesai</p></li><li data-block-id=\"f9b04ec6-cf23-48b8-8110-8f2c76be9a54\"><p data-block-id=\"06ce5eca-76e0-45e0-8c61-7737c43bec87\">Gulir ke bawah ke Bukti Pembayaran Payout dan klik Kirim Bukti Pembayaran</p></li><li data-block-id=\"753ab440-5065-40d7-8a1a-0afb408fd7ea\"><p data-block-id=\"ca238ff1-8742-4241-ba89-9fe5124707ae\">Masukkan email penerima Anda</p></li></ol><h4 data-block-id=\"c56028c6-6b5e-4654-9603-45c498ee6c11\">Batch Payouts</h4><ol data-block-id=\"8e03f680-bd9c-46e6-9708-c274f00135a6\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"17afcbf7-bb2a-4c63-9901-b0cf8d0f2940\"><p data-block-id=\"950bfd8a-4a57-49b5-95de-68f144437d00\">Buka <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/dashboard/batch_disbursements\" translate=\"no\">Batch Payouts &gt; Disetujui</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"219cd9ef-eaa2-4946-b1c1-513133371976\"><p data-block-id=\"a0366aad-aebe-434d-9718-03d7c7316074\">Klik pada sebuah batch payout</p></li><li data-block-id=\"d8353d4a-deb1-4604-bc73-e3b4ca773d01\"><p data-block-id=\"e80bd9a0-998c-4d63-94dd-d059458e99a0\">Ekspor semua atau bukti pembayaran yang dipilih</p><ol data-block-id=\"e7c2fecb-8248-469b-a6a8-44052e9a2c7c\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"96f4b0db-6dc9-4c14-a3b5-4d255653f337\"><p data-block-id=\"ee6bfdcb-a277-491c-9a0d-e45c1d498d1b\">Untuk semua: Klik Ekspor Bukti Pembayaran &gt; Semua yang Selesai</p></li><li data-block-id=\"9443c5ad-54ca-43c5-9670-4d4fb4a8234e\"><p data-block-id=\"ebd2275e-e96c-459d-8fb1-40abf7735f92\">Untuk yang dipilih: Pilih transaksi, lalu klik Ekspor Bukti Pembayaran &gt; Yang Dipilih</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"329a631a-3d5e-4c05-9da5-c47ac053a665\"><p data-block-id=\"2b396333-0089-4d42-9665-da1f0dffe304\">Tautan unduhan (berlaku selama 7 hari) akan dikirimkan melalui email kepada Anda</p></li><li data-block-id=\"7b0a2bcf-1201-4633-b7c0-330256448068\"><p data-block-id=\"665153cb-cf6f-4e4f-9518-dfbf4e07d7d2\">Buka email dan klik untuk mengunduh bukti pembayaran Anda</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"3caf28b2-b858-46f7-8280-2b144edeb637\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Optimalisasi operasional","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"การเพิ่มประสิทธิภาพการดำเนินงาน","Slug":"operations-guide","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"0d83e324-6b18-4d15-9efa-215c7ff3db88\">เรียนรู้วิธีลดข้อร้องเรียนของลูกค้าและช่วยตอบคำถามของลูกค้า หน้านี้จะแนะนำแนวทางปฏิบัติที่ดีที่สุดที่จะช่วยให้คุณบรรลุความเป็นเลิศในการดำเนินงาน (operational excellence) </p><h2 data-block-id=\"c9b5c42b-7fb9-4e9d-9ffb-f19e2b597276\">ปัญหาการดำเนินงานที่พบบ่อย</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"708aa0a6-59ab-47c7-803d-267b9cad4868\">ไม่ได้รับเงินทุน</h3><p data-block-id=\"8fed5d84-96fa-4280-82a7-c06179f1701e\">เนื่องจากปัญหาด้านการสื่อสาร ผู้รับของคุณอาจติดต่อกลับมาและแจ้งว่ายังไม่ได้รับเงินทุน เพื่อช่วยในกระบวนการนี้ เราขอแนะนำให้คุณ:</p><ul data-block-id=\"328d892c-175c-4048-bb61-99fc0e52fc9a\"><li data-block-id=\"20f947d2-6842-4a8f-823d-0495c84eaf40\"><p data-block-id=\"d6da130f-97f7-4a53-a48b-9f8eb59b5f4a\">สมัครรับ Payout webhooks เพื่อรับสถานะล่าสุดและการกู้คืนอัตโนมัติ (auto recovery)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"0ae03ab7-2e91-4d5b-80c1-3894a3cf136d\"><p data-block-id=\"547eeb2a-72ab-4914-8cef-6f594efd1907\">ส่งใบเสร็จ Payout (Payout receipt) ให้ผู้รับของคุณเพื่อติดตามและแจ้งปัญหาไปยังธนาคารของพวกเขา</p></li><li data-block-id=\"6215d941-16e6-497e-81ba-7dad28118b06\"><p data-block-id=\"2735f089-916e-4803-bb1a-cce10c82d74e\">ใช้ <code>description</code> เพื่อส่งตัวระบุ (identifiers) ไปยังแอปพลิเคชันหรือใบแจ้งยอดของผู้รับของคุณ</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"ecf72a0f-91f0-44af-adb0-74938842ddd5\">เงินทุนถูกตีกลับ</h3><p data-block-id=\"1bfa13ca-e548-4e9b-a5d4-ba31b0a62e29\">บางครั้งเราไม่สามารถจ่ายเงินทุนออกไปได้ หรือเงินทุนถูกส่งคืนกลับมาเนื่องจากข้อจำกัดในการประมวลผล (เช่น รายละเอียดของผู้รับไม่ถูกต้อง หรือบัญชีของพวกเขาถูกปิด) เราขอแนะนำให้คุณ:</p><ul data-block-id=\"b2a183d0-6f95-426c-98aa-44ddc90b04db\"><li data-block-id=\"487082c5-870e-4121-8c67-ce5d06a67d1e\"><p data-block-id=\"6627dc47-93a4-46ee-a860-beeca688ab70\">สมัครรับ reversed/failed webhooks เพื่อรับสถานะล่าสุด</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"f49c69e3-b5ec-437b-a919-6c48b6082cd2\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"8f796388-25e8-4452-aa55-ba5da3e1e6e7\">เครื่องมือสำหรับลดปัญหาการดำเนินงาน</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"7910962d-e6f6-43d5-a28c-55b7db6f5ce9\">ใบเสร็จ Payout</h3><p data-block-id=\"be7bce22-a700-4a12-9bc3-602101dd205b\">ใบเสร็จ Payout เป็นเครื่องมือที่เรียบง่ายแต่ทรงพลัง เพื่อยืนยันกับผู้รับว่าเงินทุนได้รับการประมวลผลแล้ว และหากยังไม่ได้รับ ก็กำลังจะเข้าสู่บัญชีของพวกเขา หากมีการใช้งาน เราจะส่งสิ่งนี้ในนามของคุณโดยตรงไปยังผู้รับของคุณเมื่อการประมวลผล Payout สำเร็จ</p><h4 data-block-id=\"ee899a45-9973-4b5d-8357-5537c33ca90b\">สร้างแบรนด์ให้กับใบเสร็จ Payout ของคุณเพื่อสร้างความไว้วางใจยิ่งขึ้น</h4><p data-block-id=\"bfd422d7-15cc-449f-b181-0db2e891360c\">ปรับแต่งใบเสร็จด้วยโลโก้ธุรกิจของคุณ โดยค่าเริ่มต้น โลโก้ธุรกิจในโปรไฟล์ของคุณจะถูกแสดง</p><ol data-block-id=\"760d138c-d367-4f55-8faf-68ecdaf3465e\" start=\"1\" style data-indent=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"19c726fb-f196-4fdb-b6cb-e3c75414c13f\"><p data-block-id=\"fe5911ff-a94f-46db-b7cf-1676ce3c028b\">เข้าสู่ระบบ dashboard ของคุณ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"540a84e4-f40b-40bb-bc5d-bb963010121f\"><p data-block-id=\"3cba473c-8e47-4873-93d7-b7449b968c64\">ไปที่ Settings &gt; <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/business-profile#business\" translate=\"no\">Edit Profile</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"f4f1a71f-bae0-4ba7-87a4-a0c4fa89a0f2\"><p data-block-id=\"acc1c727-c3dd-4ae8-8e94-415248fa417d\">คลิก Upload Business Logo</p></li></ol><h4 data-block-id=\"93b06bc9-41b6-4c6a-b3c6-f3ef32dafef9\">ระบุช่องทางช่วยเหลือ (helpline) สำหรับผู้ใช้ของคุณ</h4><ol data-block-id=\"99189ec8-0755-4943-a115-1b1ff2d63e20\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"3fee97e3-8dfa-4894-9569-235f0300d5a3\"><p data-block-id=\"885e025f-dad6-44a7-9880-d7eccee8164f\">เข้าสู่ระบบ dashboard ของคุณ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"d7be3adc-3a29-4c9b-9fc9-d680d6b94a0b\"><p data-block-id=\"e9066016-6eba-458e-9896-ec06087d18bd\">ไปที่ <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/sending-money#disbursement-notifications\" translate=\"no\">Disbursement Notifications Settings</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"61334aaa-c028-461b-abfd-fd23ada9c4f2\"><p data-block-id=\"e0d91721-b1c5-47e4-91e7-d328777c1aea\">ในส่วน Disbursement Email Template หรือ Batch Disbursement Email Template คุณสามารถป้อนข้อมูลที่จะแสดงให้ผู้ใช้ปลายทางเห็นในส่วนท้ายของอีเมล (email footer)</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"ffd3a5bc-bf12-4e06-a966-0e65c7c1869a\"><img data-block-id=\"4399aa04-92eb-46eb-932f-d0f3243fdaaa\" src=\"https://archive.docs.xendit.co/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fres.cloudinary.com%2Fdpvzoteik%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fc_fill%2Ch_330%2Cw_1598%2FScreenshot_2023-12-06_at_15.15.00_ws6m3c%3F_a%3DBATCr5fi0&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"1125\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border:0px solid rgb(229, 231, 235);--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-color:rgba(59,130,246,.5);--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;display:block;vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;margin-top:2em;margin-bottom:2em;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;color:transparent;width:1125px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"4e7cbae7-d6c8-4138-b08d-197b4df66e3d\"></p><h3 data-block-id=\"894aa43a-5e59-4212-be19-54e27e1a2db4\">ส่งใบเสร็จ Payout ซ้ำ</h3><p data-block-id=\"c6ac5423-f91f-4ca3-8ea4-165b7bac58d5\">สามารถส่งใบเสร็จ Payout ซ้ำได้อย่างง่ายดายจาก dashboard ของคุณ เพื่อแบ่งปันกับผู้รับเป็นหลักฐานการโอน</p><h4 data-block-id=\"f28c0e8e-31f2-457c-9f89-32b608b0cda1\">Payouts API</h4><ol data-block-id=\"7d0e64a7-d224-4212-a81e-41e2a62b32eb\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"298b8f1b-cb8d-4e9a-b2fa-45d96d7a0e2a\"><p data-block-id=\"93f4e629-2433-4eb9-b025-c2aededbd6cd\">ไปที่ <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/transactions-new\" translate=\"no\">Transactions</a> บน dashboard ของคุณ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"76f1a087-ec25-4634-bcdc-4d65bc887d60\"><p data-block-id=\"9a3989bd-b2e5-4173-86ae-94ab3a53bb9f\">คลิกที่รายการธุรกรรมที่เสร็จสมบูรณ์</p></li><li data-block-id=\"f9b04ec6-cf23-48b8-8110-8f2c76be9a54\"><p data-block-id=\"06ce5eca-76e0-45e0-8c61-7737c43bec87\">เลื่อนลงไปที่ Payout Receipt และคลิก Send Receipt</p></li><li data-block-id=\"753ab440-5065-40d7-8a1a-0afb408fd7ea\"><p data-block-id=\"ca238ff1-8742-4241-ba89-9fe5124707ae\">ป้อนอีเมลของผู้รับของคุณ</p></li></ol><h4 data-block-id=\"c56028c6-6b5e-4654-9603-45c498ee6c11\">Batch Payouts</h4><ol data-block-id=\"8e03f680-bd9c-46e6-9708-c274f00135a6\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"17afcbf7-bb2a-4c63-9901-b0cf8d0f2940\"><p data-block-id=\"950bfd8a-4a57-49b5-95de-68f144437d00\">ไปที่ <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/dashboard/batch_disbursements\" translate=\"no\">Batch Payouts &gt; Approved</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"219cd9ef-eaa2-4946-b1c1-513133371976\"><p data-block-id=\"a0366aad-aebe-434d-9718-03d7c7316074\">คลิกที่รายการ Batch Payout</p></li><li data-block-id=\"d8353d4a-deb1-4604-bc73-e3b4ca773d01\"><p data-block-id=\"e80bd9a0-998c-4d63-94dd-d059458e99a0\">ส่งออกใบเสร็จทั้งหมดหรือที่เลือก</p><ol data-block-id=\"e7c2fecb-8248-469b-a6a8-44052e9a2c7c\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"96f4b0db-6dc9-4c14-a3b5-4d255653f337\"><p data-block-id=\"ee6bfdcb-a277-491c-9a0d-e45c1d498d1b\">สำหรับทั้งหมด: คลิก Export Receipt &gt; All Completed</p></li><li data-block-id=\"9443c5ad-54ca-43c5-9670-4d4fb4a8234e\"><p data-block-id=\"ebd2275e-e96c-459d-8fb1-40abf7735f92\">สำหรับรายการที่เลือก: เลือกรายการธุรกรรม จากนั้นคลิก Export Receipt &gt; Selected</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"329a631a-3d5e-4c05-9da5-c47ac053a665\"><p data-block-id=\"2b396333-0089-4d42-9665-da1f0dffe304\">ลิงก์ดาวน์โหลด (ใช้งานได้ 7 วัน) จะถูกส่งไปยังอีเมลของคุณ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"7b0a2bcf-1201-4633-b7c0-330256448068\"><p data-block-id=\"665153cb-cf6f-4e4f-9518-dfbf4e07d7d2\">เปิดอีเมลและคลิกเพื่อดาวน์โหลดใบเสร็จของคุณ</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"3caf28b2-b858-46f7-8280-2b144edeb637\"></p>","SeoTitle":"การเพิ่มประสิทธิภาพการดำเนินงาน","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Optimizando operaciones","Slug":"optimizing-operations","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"0d83e324-6b18-4d15-9efa-215c7ff3db88\">Aprenda cómo reducir las quejas de sus clientes y ayudar con las consultas de sus clientes. Esta página le guiará a través de algunas mejores prácticas que le permitirán alcanzar la excelencia operativa. </p><h2 data-block-id=\"c9b5c42b-7fb9-4e9d-9ffb-f19e2b597276\">Problemas operativos comunes</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"708aa0a6-59ab-47c7-803d-267b9cad4868\">Fondos no recibidos</h3><p data-block-id=\"8fed5d84-96fa-4280-82a7-c06179f1701e\">Debido a problemas de mensajería, su destinatario podría contactarle diciendo que los fondos no han sido recibidos. Para ayudar con este proceso, le recomendamos que:</p><ul data-block-id=\"328d892c-175c-4048-bb61-99fc0e52fc9a\"><li data-block-id=\"20f947d2-6842-4a8f-823d-0495c84eaf40\"><p data-block-id=\"d6da130f-97f7-4a53-a48b-9f8eb59b5f4a\">Suscríbase a los webhooks de Payout para obtener las últimas actualizaciones de estado y recuperación automática</p></li><li data-block-id=\"0ae03ab7-2e91-4d5b-80c1-3894a3cf136d\"><p data-block-id=\"547eeb2a-72ab-4914-8cef-6f594efd1907\">Envíe el recibo de Payout a su destinatario para que pueda rastrear y registrar un problema con su Banco</p></li><li data-block-id=\"6215d941-16e6-497e-81ba-7dad28118b06\"><p data-block-id=\"2735f089-916e-4803-bb1a-cce10c82d74e\">Utilice <code>description</code> para enviar identificadores a la aplicación o estado de cuenta de su destinatario</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"ecf72a0f-91f0-44af-adb0-74938842ddd5\">Fondos devueltos</h3><p data-block-id=\"1bfa13ca-e548-4e9b-a5d4-ba31b0a62e29\">A veces no podemos pagar los fondos o los fondos nos son devueltos debido a limitaciones de procesamiento (por ejemplo, los detalles del destinatario eran incorrectos o su Cuenta está cerrada). Le recomendamos que:</p><ul data-block-id=\"b2a183d0-6f95-426c-98aa-44ddc90b04db\"><li data-block-id=\"487082c5-870e-4121-8c67-ce5d06a67d1e\"><p data-block-id=\"6627dc47-93a4-46ee-a860-beeca688ab70\">Suscríbase a los webhooks de reversión/fallidos para obtener las últimas actualizaciones de estado</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"f49c69e3-b5ec-437b-a919-6c48b6082cd2\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"8f796388-25e8-4452-aa55-ba5da3e1e6e7\">Herramienta para reducir problemas operativos</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"7910962d-e6f6-43d5-a28c-55b7db6f5ce9\">Recibos de Payout</h3><p data-block-id=\"be7bce22-a700-4a12-9bc3-602101dd205b\">Los recibos de Payout son una herramienta simple pero poderosa para asegurar a su destinatario que los fondos han sido procesados y, si aún no se han recibido, están en camino a su Cuenta. Si se utiliza, lo enviaremos en su nombre directamente a su destinatario al procesar el Payout exitosamente.</p><h4 data-block-id=\"ee899a45-9973-4b5d-8357-5537c33ca90b\">Personalice su recibo de Payout para generar más confianza</h4><p data-block-id=\"bfd422d7-15cc-449f-b181-0db2e891360c\">Personalice los recibos con el logo de su Comercio. Por defecto, se mostrará el logo del Comercio en su perfil.</p><ol data-block-id=\"760d138c-d367-4f55-8faf-68ecdaf3465e\" start=\"1\" style data-indent=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"19c726fb-f196-4fdb-b6cb-e3c75414c13f\"><p data-block-id=\"fe5911ff-a94f-46db-b7cf-1676ce3c028b\">Inicie sesión en su dashboard</p></li><li data-block-id=\"540a84e4-f40b-40bb-bc5d-bb963010121f\"><p data-block-id=\"3cba473c-8e47-4873-93d7-b7449b968c64\">Vaya a Configuración &gt; <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/business-profile#business\" translate=\"no\">Editar Perfil</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"f4f1a71f-bae0-4ba7-87a4-a0c4fa89a0f2\"><p data-block-id=\"acc1c727-c3dd-4ae8-8e94-415248fa417d\">Haga clic en Cargar Logo del Comercio</p></li></ol><h4 data-block-id=\"93b06bc9-41b6-4c6a-b3c6-f3ef32dafef9\">Proporcione una línea de ayuda para sus usuarios</h4><ol data-block-id=\"99189ec8-0755-4943-a115-1b1ff2d63e20\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"3fee97e3-8dfa-4894-9569-235f0300d5a3\"><p data-block-id=\"885e025f-dad6-44a7-9880-d7eccee8164f\">Inicie sesión en su dashboard</p></li><li data-block-id=\"d7be3adc-3a29-4c9b-9fc9-d680d6b94a0b\"><p data-block-id=\"e9066016-6eba-458e-9896-ec06087d18bd\">Vaya a <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/sending-money#disbursement-notifications\" translate=\"no\">Configuración de Notificaciones de Disbursement</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"61334aaa-c028-461b-abfd-fd23ada9c4f2\"><p data-block-id=\"e0d91721-b1c5-47e4-91e7-d328777c1aea\">En la sección Plantilla de Correo electrónico de Disbursement o Plantilla de Correo electrónico de Batch Disbursement, puede ingresar la información que se muestra al usuario final en el pie de página del correo electrónico</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"ffd3a5bc-bf12-4e06-a966-0e65c7c1869a\"><img data-block-id=\"4399aa04-92eb-46eb-932f-d0f3243fdaaa\" src=\"https://archive.docs.xendit.co/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fres.cloudinary.com%2Fdpvzoteik%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fc_fill%2Ch_330%2Cw_1598%2FScreenshot_2023-12-06_at_15.15.00_ws6m3c%3F_a%3DBATCr5fi0&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border:0px solid rgb(229, 231, 235);--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-color:rgba(59,130,246,.5);--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;display:block;vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;margin-top:2em;margin-bottom:2em;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;color:transparent;width:1125px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"4e7cbae7-d6c8-4138-b08d-197b4df66e3d\"></p><h3 data-block-id=\"894aa43a-5e59-4212-be19-54e27e1a2db4\">Reenviar recibos de Payout</h3><p data-block-id=\"c6ac5423-f91f-4ca3-8ea4-165b7bac58d5\">Reenvíe fácilmente los recibos de Payout desde su dashboard para compartir con los destinatarios como prueba de Transferencia.</p><h4 data-block-id=\"f28c0e8e-31f2-457c-9f89-32b608b0cda1\">API de Payouts</h4><ol data-block-id=\"7d0e64a7-d224-4212-a81e-41e2a62b32eb\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"298b8f1b-cb8d-4e9a-b2fa-45d96d7a0e2a\"><p data-block-id=\"93f4e629-2433-4eb9-b025-c2aededbd6cd\">Vaya a <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/transactions-new\" translate=\"no\">Transacciones</a> en su dashboard</p></li><li data-block-id=\"76f1a087-ec25-4634-bcdc-4d65bc887d60\"><p data-block-id=\"9a3989bd-b2e5-4173-86ae-94ab3a53bb9f\">Haga clic en la Transacción completada</p></li><li data-block-id=\"f9b04ec6-cf23-48b8-8110-8f2c76be9a54\"><p data-block-id=\"06ce5eca-76e0-45e0-8c61-7737c43bec87\">Desplácese hasta Recibo de Payout y haga clic en Enviar Recibo</p></li><li data-block-id=\"753ab440-5065-40d7-8a1a-0afb408fd7ea\"><p data-block-id=\"ca238ff1-8742-4241-ba89-9fe5124707ae\">Ingrese el correo electrónico de su destinatario</p></li></ol><h4 data-block-id=\"c56028c6-6b5e-4654-9603-45c498ee6c11\">Batch Payouts</h4><ol data-block-id=\"8e03f680-bd9c-46e6-9708-c274f00135a6\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"17afcbf7-bb2a-4c63-9901-b0cf8d0f2940\"><p data-block-id=\"950bfd8a-4a57-49b5-95de-68f144437d00\">Vaya a <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/dashboard/batch_disbursements\" translate=\"no\">Batch Payouts > Aprobados</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"219cd9ef-eaa2-4946-b1c1-513133371976\"><p data-block-id=\"a0366aad-aebe-434d-9718-03d7c7316074\">Haga clic en un Batch Payout</p></li><li data-block-id=\"d8353d4a-deb1-4604-bc73-e3b4ca773d01\"><p data-block-id=\"e80bd9a0-998c-4d63-94dd-d059458e99a0\">Exportar todos o los recibos seleccionados</p><ol data-block-id=\"e7c2fecb-8248-469b-a6a8-44052e9a2c7c\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"96f4b0db-6dc9-4c14-a3b5-4d255653f337\"><p data-block-id=\"ee6bfdcb-a277-491c-9a0d-e45c1d498d1b\">Para todos: Haga clic en Exportar Recibo > Todos Completados</p></li><li data-block-id=\"9443c5ad-54ca-43c5-9670-4d4fb4a8234e\"><p data-block-id=\"ebd2275e-e96c-459d-8fb1-40abf7735f92\">Para seleccionados: Seleccione Transacciones, luego haga clic en Exportar Recibo > Seleccionados</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"329a631a-3d5e-4c05-9da5-c47ac053a665\"><p data-block-id=\"2b396333-0089-4d42-9665-da1f0dffe304\">Se le enviará por correo electrónico un enlace de descarga (válido por 7 días)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"7b0a2bcf-1201-4633-b7c0-330256448068\"><p data-block-id=\"665153cb-cf6f-4e4f-9518-dfbf4e07d7d2\">Abra el correo electrónico y haga clic para descargar su(s) recibo(s)</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"3caf28b2-b858-46f7-8280-2b144edeb637\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Optimizando operaciones","Description":null}]